      the bottom of the screen (you need an Internet connection only to do that).
  </p>' WHERE `pc_translation`.`language_id` = 'en' AND `pc_translation`.`string_id` = 'WEBSITE_SERVICES_SMARTPHONE_APP_BODY3';

